description: TEHRAN – The Islamic Revolution Guards Corps (IRGC) on Thursday dismissed as a “big lie” that the building of Israel’s Dimona nuclear facility has suffered damages in Iran’s legitimate defense against Israel on April 13, calling it a “psychological warfare” intended to deceive the public opinion.
title: Iran says claims of damage to Dimona nuclear facility is a psychological warfare

description: TEHRAN - An IRGC official in charge of nuclear protection and security threatened on Thursday that if Israel launches attack on Iran's nuclear facilities, the Zionist regime will surely face "tit-for-tat" retaliation with “advanced weapons” by the Islamic Republic.
title: IRGC threatens ‘tit-for-tat’ retaliation if Israel targets Iranian nuclear sites

description: Persepolis football team provisionally moved top of 2023/24 Iran's Persian Gulf Pro League (PGPL) on Thursday.
title: Persepolis move provisionally top of PGPL

title: Iran beat Afghanistan at 2024 AFC Futsal Asian Cup opener
